commits.content:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <!-- Custom fonts for this template-->
    <link href="{{ url_for('static', filename='vendor/img/svg/logo.svg')}}" type="image/x-icon">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Nunito:200,200i,300,300i,400,400i,600,600i,700,700i,800,800i,900,900i" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Custom styles for this template-->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/style.min.css')}}" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/style.css')}}" rel="stylesheet"> {% block title %}{% endblock %}
</head>

<body>
    {% block content %}{% endblock %}
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <!-- Core plugin JavaScript-->
    {% block js %}
    <script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='plugins/chart.min.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='plugins/feather.min.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='js/script.js') }}"></script>
    {% endblock %}
</body>

</html>
